<p>Once you have successfully linked your account, click on Connect to Twitch in your Receiver to test your connection (Transmitter must be running).</p>

<p>You should see these following yellow notification messages and it is important to check that ALL of these messages actually come up:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Twitch is connected</li>
  <li>Listening for Channel points</li>
  <li>Listening for Bits donations</li>
  <li>Listening for Channel subscriptions</li>
  <li>Listening for Chat Moderation</li>
  <li>Connected to Twitch chat.</li>
</ul>

<p>Congratulations, your Twitch account is now connected</p>
